textAnnotations.description:
To be restored - 1971 Reliant Scimitar SES
After years of neglect, this Scimitar will be subject to a
full "body off" restoration; returning it to its' former glony!
The restoration will be documented and published in
Slice magazine, the members magazine for the RSSOC
(Reliant Sabre & Scimitar Owners Club).
For more information on joining, or Scimitars visit
www.scimitarweb.com
